@mihob @samdark There doesn't seem to be a function `FileHelper::getExtensionByMimeType` only the function `FileHelper::getExtensionsByMimeType` (note the plural "Extensions") exists. Which is logical since one mime type can have multiple extensions.
@mihob Are you using a custom function?

Please see #19838 for an actual implementation of `FileHelper::getExtensionByMimeType()`.
